#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_website_event_track
msgid ""
"Organize Events, Trainings & Webinars\n"
"-------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Schedule, Promote, Sell, Organize\n"
"\n"
"Get extra features per event; multiple pages, sponsors, multiple talks, talk proposal form, agenda, event-related news, documents (slides of presentations), event-specific menus.\n"
"\n"
"Organize Your Tracks\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"### From the talk proposal to the publication\n"
"\n"
"Add a talk proposal form on your events to allow visitors to submit talks and speakers. Organize the validation process of every talk, and schedule easily.\n"
"\n"
"DTCloud's unique frontend and backend integration makes organization and publication so easy. Easily design beautiful speaker biographies and talks description.\n"
"\n"
"Agenda and List of Talks\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### A strong user interface\n"
"\n"
"Get a beautiful agenda for each event published automatically on your website. Allow your visitors to easily search and browse talks, filter by tags, locations or speakers.\n"
"\n"
"Manage Sponsors\n"
"---------------\n"
"\n"
"### Sell sponsorship, promote your sponsors\n"
"\n"
"Add sponsors to your events and publish sponsors per level (e.g. bronze, silver, gold) on the bottom of every page of the event.\n"
"\n"
"Sell sponsorship packages online through the DTCloud eCommerce for a full sales cycle integration.\n"
"\n"
"Communicate Efficiently\n"
"-----------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Activate a blog for some events\n"
"\n"
"You can activate a blog for each event allowing you to communicate on specific events. Visitors can subscribe to news to get informed."
msgstr ""
"组织活动、培训和网络研讨会\n"
"-------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 安排、推广、销售、组织\n"
"\n"
"获得每个活动的额外功能；多个页面、赞助商、多次会谈、会谈提案表、议程、与活动相关的新闻、文档（演示文稿幻灯片）以及活动特定的菜单。\n"
"\n"
"跟进您的活动\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 从会谈提案到发布\n"
"\n"
"在活动中添加谈话提案表，允许访客提交会谈内容和发言人。组织每次会谈的验证流程，并轻松安排时间。\n"
"\n"
"DTCloud 独特的前端和后端集成使组织和发布变得非常简单。轻松设计精美的发言人简介和会谈描述。\n"
"\n"
"议程和会谈列表\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 强大的用户界面\n"
"\n"
"为网站上自动发布的每个活动安排详细的议程。允许访客轻松搜索和浏览会谈，按标签、位置或发言人进行筛选。\n"
"\n"
"管理赞助商\n"
"---------------\n"
"\n"
"### 推销赞助商，宣传赞助商\n"
"\n"
"添加赞助商到您的活动并在活动的每一页底部发布各个级别的赞助商（例如铜级、白银级、黄金级）。\n"
"\n"
"通过 DTCloud 电子商城在线销售赞助套餐，实现整个销售周期的集成。\n"
"\n"
"有效沟通\n"
"-----------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 针对一些活动开通博客\n"
"\n"
"您可以针对每个活动开通博客，以便在特定活动中进行沟通。访客可以订阅新闻以获得消息。"

#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_website_event
msgid ""
"Organize Events, Trainings & Webinars\n"
"-------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Schedule, Promote, Sell, Organize\n"
"\n"
"Organize, promote and sell events online. Whether you organize meetings, conferences, trainings or webinars, DTCloud gives you all the features you need to manage your events.\n"
"\n"
"Create Awesome Event Pages\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Get rid of old WYSIWYG editors\n"
"\n"
"Create beautiful event pages by drag & droping well designed *'Building Blocks'*. Publish event photos, speakers, schedule, etc.\n"
"\n"
"DTCloud's unique *'edit inline'* approach makes website creation surprisingly easy. \"Want to introduce a speaker? to change the price of a ticket? to update a banner? promote sponsors?\" just click and change.\n"
"\n"
"Sell Tickets Online\n"
"-------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Automate the registration and payment process\n"
"\n"
"Sell registrations to your event with the multi-ticketing feature. Events can be free or for a fee. Attendees can pay online with a credit card or on invoice, based on your configuration.\n"
"\n"
"Boost your sales with early-bird prices, special conditions for members, or extra services with multiple tickets.\n"
"\n"
"A Clean Google Analytics Integration\n"
"------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Control your sales funnel with Google Analytics\n"
"\n"
"Get a clear visibility of your sales funnel. DTCloud's Google Analytics trackers are configured by default to track all kind of events related to shopping carts, call-to-actions, etc.\n"
"\n"
"As DTCloud marketing tools (mass mailing, campaigns, etc) are also linked with Google Analytics, you get a full view of your business.\n"
"\n"
"Promote Events Efficiently\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Mass Mailing & Social Media\n"
"\n"
"Use the segmentation, the social network integration and mass mailing features to promote your events to the right audience. Setup automated emails to attendees to send them last minute details.\n"
"\n"
"Designer-Friendly Themes\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Designers love working on DTCloud\n"
"\n"
"Themes are awesome and easy to design. You don't need to develop to create new pages, themes or building blocks. We use a clean HTML structure, a [bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com/) CSS and our modularity allows to distribute your themes easily.\n"
"\n"
"The building block approach allows the website to stay clean after the end-users start creating new contents.\n"
"\n"
"Make Your Event More Visible\n"
"----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### SEO tools at your finger tips\n"
"\n"
"SEO tools are ready to use, with no configuration required. DTCloud suggests keywords according to Google most searched terms, Google Analytics tracks your shopping cart events and sitemap are created automatically.\n"
"\n"
"We even do structured content automatically to promote your events and products efficiently in Google.\n"
"\n"
"Leverage Social Media\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Optimize: from Ads to Conversions\n"
"\n"
"Create new landing pages easily with the DTCloud inline editing feature. Send visitors of your different marketing campaigns to event landing pages to optimize conversions.\n"
"\n"
"And Much More...\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"### Schedule\n"
"\n"
"-   Calendar of Events\n"
"-   Publish related documents\n"
"-   Ressources allocation\n"
"-   Automate purchases (catering...)\n"
"-   Multiple locations and organizers\n"
"-   Mobile Interface\n"
"\n"
"### Sell\n"
"\n"
"-   Online or offline sales\n"
"-   Automated invoicing\n"
"-   Cancellation policies\n"
"-   Specific prices for members\n"
"-   Dashboards and reporting\n"
"\n"
"### Organize\n"
"\n"
"-   Advanced Planification\n"
"-   Print Badges\n"
"-   Automate Follow-up Emails\n"
"-   Min/Max capacities\n"
"-   Manage classes and ressources\n"
"-   Create group of attendees\n"
"-   Automate statisfaction surveys\n"
"\n"
"Fully Integrated With Others Apps\n"
"---------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Get hundreds of open source apps for free\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### eCommerce\n"
"\n"
"Promote products, sell online, optimize visitors' shopping experiences.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Blogs\n"
"\n"
"Write news, attract new visitors, build customer loyalty.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Our Team\n"
"\n"
"Create a great \"About us\" page by presenting your team efficiently.\n"
msgstr ""
"组织活动、培训和网络研讨会\n"
"-------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 安排、推广、推销、组织\n"
"\n"
"在线组织、推广和推销活动。无论您是组织会议、培训还是网络研讨会，DTCloud 都能为您提供管理活动所需的所有功能。\n"
"\n"
"创建绝佳的活动页面\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 摆脱过时的 WYSIWYG 编辑器\n"
"\n"
"通过拖放精心设计的 *“构建块”* 创建精美的活动页面。发布活动照片、发言人、时间表等。\n"
"\n"
"DTCloud 独特的 *“行内编辑”* 方法使网站创建变得非常简单。“想要介绍一位发言人？改变票价？更新标语？宣传赞助商？”只需点击一下即可更改。\n"
"\n"
"在线售票\n"
"-------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 自动化注册和支付流程\n"
"\n"
"通过“多重开票”功能出售活动的注册权。活动既可以免费，也可以收费。参与者可以根据您的配置使用信用卡或凭结算单在线支付。\n"
"\n"
"通过早买优惠价格、会员特殊条款或购买多张门票提供额外服务等方法提高您的销售量。\n"
"\n"
"简洁的 Google Analytics 集成\n"
"------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 使用 Google Analytics 掌控您的销售渠道\n"
"\n"
"清楚了解您的销售渠道。DTCloud 的 Google Analytics 跟踪器默认配置为跟踪与购物车、号召性行动等相关的所有活动。\n"
"\n"
"由于 DTCloud 市场营销工具（群发邮件、营销活动等）也与 Google Analytics 相关联，因此您可以全面了解您的业务。\n"
"\n"
"有效推广活动\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 群发邮件和社交媒体\n"
"\n"
"使用细分、社交网络集成和群发邮件功能，将您的活动推广给合适的受众。设置自动发送电子邮件以便向参与者发送关键细节。\n"
"\n"
"设计人员友好主题\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 设计人员热衷于使用 DTCloud 办公\n"
"\n"
"主题非常棒，且易于设计。无需进一步开发就可创建新的页面、主题或构建块。我们使用简洁的 HTML 结构和 [bootstrap] (http://getbootstrap.com/) CSS，并且通过我们的模块化可以轻松分配您的主题。\n"
"\n"
"使用构建块方法，这样终端用户做修改时候，也仍可以保持系统整洁。\n"
"\n"
"提高活动的受关注度\n"
"----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"###SEO 工具触手可及\n"
"\n"
"SEO 工具即时可用，无需配置。DTCloud 根据 Google 中搜索最多的词汇推荐关键字，Google Analytics 跟踪您的购物车活动，并且自动创建站点地图。\n"
"\n"
"我们还会自动设置结构化内容，以便在 Google 中有效推广您的活动和产品。\n"
"\n"
"利用社交媒体\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 优化：从广告到转化\n"
"\n"
"使用 DTCloud 行内编辑功能轻松创建新的登录页面。将不同市场营销活动的访客发送到活动目标网页以优化转化。\n"
"\n"
"更多内容...\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"### 安排\n"
"\n"
"- 活动日志\n"
"- 发布相关文档\n"
"- 资源分配\n"
"- 自动采购（餐饮...）\n"
"- 多个地点和组织者\n"
"- 移动界面\n"
"\n"
"### 销售\n"
"\n"
"- 在线或离线销售\n"
"- 自动开票\n"
"- 取消政策\n"
"- 会员特定价格\n"
"- 仪表板和报表\n"
"\n"
"### 组织\n"
"\n"
"- 高级计划\n"
"- 打印徽章\n"
"- 自动发送跟进电子邮件\n"
"- 最小/最大容量\n"
"- 管理分类和资源\n"
"- 创建参与者群组\n"
"- 自动化满意度调查问卷\n"
"\n"
"完全与其他应用集成\n"
"---------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### 免费获得数百个开源应用程序\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### 电子商务\n"
"\n"
"推广产品、在线销售、优化访客的购物体验。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### 博客\n"
"\n"
"撰写新闻、吸引新访客、建立客户忠诚度。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### 我们的团队\n"
"\n"
"创建出色的“关于我们”页面，高效地展示您的团队。\n"

